title: Ohio Senator Jon Husted voted to block Epstein files after donation from Leslie Wexner: Report
summary_full: Ohio Republican Senator Jon Husted is under scrutiny for voting to block the release of Jeffrey Epstein files shortly after receiving a $3,500 campaign donation from Leslie Wexner, a former associate of the convicted sex offender. This donation is part of over $116,000 Husted has received from Wexner throughout his career.
